title: Let's unf**k the planet, one YouTube Short at a time #UnFckItChallenge #shorts
author: YouTube
description:
Let’s unf**k the planet, one video at a time.

Here’s the challenge: 
1) Grab your phone. 
2) Make a YouTube Short sharing a “before” and “after”—i.e. one simple thing to heal the Earth. 
Example: trash to composting. Textile waste to upcycling. Any problem to any simple solution! 
3) Search for the challenge song “Can't You See Remix #UnFckItChallenge” in the YouTube Shorts music library.
4) Use #UnFckItChallenge in the title of your Short so it’s sure to be counted.

Little things add up. Let’s do this.

To see everything that YouTube and Google are doing to create a more sustainable Earth, please visit https://sustainability.google/.
